.DS_Store

# Runtime scratch
# NOTE: state/ AND output/ are committed durable stores — the service cron
# writes output/<lead>/variations.json and the poll cron (a fresh checkout)
# reads it to build the Gmail draft, so it must persist in the repo.
*.violations.txt

# Google token cache (never commit credentials)
token.json
client_secret*.json
service_account*.json
